Giving

 

	In February, ICS celebrated the first anniversary of the Kleist Chair in Informatics by honoring Bob and Barbara Kleist for their generous donation. According to the Kleists, “We wanted to make a difference, like many others, and an endowed chair will provide ongoing support for medical informatics, which means ongoing support for younger generations at ICS."
 

                             
                            












